---
export const prerender = true;

import PageShell from "../components/layout/PageShell.astro";

const lastUpdated = "April 17, 2026";
---

<PageShell
  title="Terms of Service — ForzaTunes"
  description="Terms of Service for ForzaTunes."
  canonicalUrl="/terms"
>
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-gray max-w-none space-y-8 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using ForzaTunes ("the Service"), you agree to be bound by
          these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">2. Description of Service</h2>
        <p>
          ForzaTunes is a free, open-source, community-run site where users can share
          and discover tune share codes for the Forza series of video games. ForzaTunes
          is not affiliated with Microsoft, Xbox Game Studios, Turn 10 Studios, or
          Playground Games.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">3. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>
          You sign in via Discord OAuth. You are responsible for keeping your Discord
          account secure. We may suspend or terminate accounts that abuse the Service,
          post prohibited content, or harm the community.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">4. User Content</h2>
        <p>
          You retain ownership of the content you submit (tune share codes, titles,
          descriptions, gamertags). By submitting content you grant ForzaTunes a
          worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to host, display, and
          redistribute it solely to operate the Service.
        </p>
        <p>You agree not to submit content that:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-400">
          <li>Is illegal, infringing, harassing, hateful, or defamatory.</li>
          <li>Contains personal information about others without consent.</li>
          <li>Advertises commercial products or services.</li>
          <li>Abuses the submission system (duplicates, spam, farm accounts).</li>
          <li>Violates Microsoft's Game Content Usage Rules or any third-party rights.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          We may remove any content for any reason at our sole discretion, including
          to comply with legal requests or to protect the community.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">5. Reports and Moderation</h2>
        <p>
          You may report tunes that violate these terms. Reports are reviewed by site
          moderators. Abusive or bad-faith reporting may result in account restrictions.
          Moderation decisions are final.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">6. Microsoft Game Content Usage Rules</h2>
        <p>
          ForzaTunes operates under Microsoft's Game Content Usage Rules.
          "Forza Horizon," "Forza Motorsport," associated logos, vehicle names, track
          names, and game assets are trademarks or intellectual property of Microsoft
          Corporation and/or its licensors. ForzaTunes does not claim ownership of
          any such assets and does not represent itself as an official Microsoft,
          Turn 10, or Playground Games product.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          The ForzaTunes source code is made available under its open-source license
          as stated in the project's GitHub repository. Third-party trademarks and
          assets remain the property of their respective owners.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">8. Prohibited Use</h2>
        <p>You may not:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-400">
          <li>Scrape, crawl, or harvest the Service in a way that disrupts operation.</li>
          <li>Attempt to bypass rate limits, authentication, or moderation controls.</li>
          <li>Use the Service to deliver malware or malicious payloads.</li>
          <li>Impersonate other users or misrepresent your affiliation.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">9. Disclaimers</h2>
        <p>
          The Service is provided "as is" and "as available," without warranties of
          any kind. We do not guarantee that any tune will work as described or will
          be free of errors. Use any submitted tune at your own risk — ForzaTunes is
          not responsible for in-game results, losses, or damage.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, ForzaTunes and its contributors
          shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential,
          or punitive damages arising from your use of the Service.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">11. Termination</h2>
        <p>
          We may suspend or terminate your access to the Service at any time, with or
          without notice, for any reason, including violation of these Terms. You may
          stop using the Service and request account deletion at any time.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">12. Changes to These Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We may update these Terms as the project evolves. Material changes will be
          communicated on the site. Continued use after changes constitutes acceptance
          of the updated Terms.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-heading font-semibold text-white">13. Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Open an issue on
          <a href="https://github.com/forzatunes/forzatunes/issues" target="_blank"
             rel="noopener noreferrer"
             class="text-accent-400 hover:text-accent-300 underline">GitHub</a>
          for questions or concerns.
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</PageShell>
